				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Nasty monsters. The main problem with them is their fire shield which will cause damage with every hit that you score. Furthermore they burn you good with aggressive spells. I soloed one that conned blue to me, but it cost me 400 HP to stomp him. If you are not in a group with a bard or a cleric (or other kind of healer), just forget them. But beware.. they are aggressive and will train in the most unpleasant moments.
