				A bit more info on the dirty little imps...<BR>
as far as lvl 16-20 goes, i don't think that's terribly true since all through level 14 and 15 i never once saw one con any worse than even and even that was rare... though given they do fight much tougher than they con. Also, as far as loot goes, i've gotten various stones off of them (mostly bloodstones) and ashroot in addition to coins. If they are blue to you i would suggest only fighting them if you have another person helping you out or cross your fingers and hope for a lucky round. I've been slaughtered enough times by these bois and taken revenge upon them enough to know... hope this helps ;)<BR>
