				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I am a Druidess 17th hunting in ls and here are my<BR>
observations reguarding these creatures:  If you <BR>
are a druid and have both endure fire and expulse<BR>
summoned you can EASILY solo these monsters if <BR>
they are green or blue.  You may also solo the <BR>
black or yellow ones if you stay close to naj <BR>
gates so you may zone.  I have killed 3 yellow<BR>
ones in 5 attempts being fully buffed and using<BR>
expulse summoned while meleeing them with my ebm.<BR>
When in doubt, pull them near naj gates. I leveled<BR>
through 14-16 grouping and soloing there and now <BR>
soloing at lvl 17.  Good hunting!  If you see me<BR>
online tell me for a SOW!
				</font>
